<text><body>
<lb n="0310c14"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0310c15"/>
<lb n="0310c16"/><head type="no">No. 954B</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0310c17"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0310060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】明本，此經麗宋元三本無之，【甲】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本</note>一字頂輪王念誦儀軌<note place="inline">依忉利天宮所說經譯</note></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0310c18"/>
<lb n="0310c19"/><p>我今說無比力超勝世間出世間真言上上。
<lb n="0310c20"/>一切佛頂<note n="0310061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王佛＝主宰一字&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0310061"><lem>王佛</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">主宰一字</rdg></app>頂輪王念誦儀則。行者先當
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0954B.0311a" n="0311a"/>
<lb n="0311a01"/>清淨。於淨處安本尊像。面西稽首禮。受三歸
<lb n="0311a02"/>捨身說罪受戒。發菩提心隨喜勸請發願&CB00327;
<lb n="0311a03"/>向已。應結佛部三昧耶印。四頂互內交。二輪
<lb n="0311a04"/>並合&CB00594;。前附於蓋。是名一切如來心印真言
<lb n="0311a05"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0311a06"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引一</note>邇那匿<note place="inline">而翼切二</note></p>
<lb n="0311a07"/><p>次結蓮<note n="0311001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">華＋（部）【甲】</note><app n="0311001"><lem>華</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">華部</rdg></app>三昧耶印。即前印。左輪屈入掌
<lb n="0311a08"/>中。右輪如前&CB00594;。是名蓮華部心印真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0311a09"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引一</note>阿嚕力<note place="inline">二</note></p>
<lb n="0311a10"/><p>次結金剛部三昧耶印。即前蓮華部心印。右
<lb n="0311a11"/>輪屈入掌中。左輪依前&CB00594;。是名金剛部心印
<lb n="0311a12"/>真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0311a13"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引一</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>地力<note place="inline">二合二</note></p>
<lb n="0311a14"/><p>次結甲冑印准根本印。屈二蓋拄二光。背印
<lb n="0311a15"/>額右肩左肩心喉五處。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0311a16"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引一</note>斫羯囉<note place="inline">二合</note>靺&CB00069;底<note place="inline">二合二</note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>賒弭多
<lb n="0311a17"/><note place="inline">三</note>囉捺囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>囉捺囉<note place="inline">二合引四</note>婆<note place="inline">去聲</note>娑摩<note place="inline">二合</note>車盧
<lb n="0311a18"/>瑟尼<note place="inline">二合</note>沙<note place="inline">五</note>囉乞沙<note place="inline">二合</note>囉乞沙<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0311002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鋡＝&CB00805;【甲】</note><note n="0311002" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="c"/>鋡＝&CB00805;【甲】</note>&CB00805;<note place="inline">六</note>吽
<lb n="0311a19"/>癹娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合合</note>訶<note place="inline">引七</note></p>
<lb n="0311a20"/><p>次結佛眼印。二手合掌。屈二蓋各拄光背。二
<lb n="0311a21"/>輪屈入掌。印五處真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0311a22"/><p type="dharani">娜<note n="0311003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謨＝莫【甲】＊</note><app n="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>唵<note place="inline">引二</note>嚕嚕薩怖<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0311a23"/>嚕<note place="inline">三</note>入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00256;底瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合四</note>悉馱盧者寧<note place="inline">五</note>薩
<lb n="0311a24"/>&CB00085;喇他<note place="inline">二合</note>娑達尼娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引六</note></p>
<lb n="0311a25"/><p>次結大海印。二手內相叉。仰掌擘開二輪。右
<lb n="0311a26"/>旋三匝想大海真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0311a27"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引一</note>微摩盧娜地娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引二</note></p>
<lb n="0311a28"/><p>次於大海中想須彌盧山。四寶所成。二手內
<lb n="0311a29"/>相叉急握豎拳真言曰。</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0954B.0311b" n="0311b"/>
<lb n="0311b01"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引一</note>阿者&CB00256;吽<note place="inline">二</note></p>
<lb n="0311b02"/><p>次於須彌盧山上想寶樓閣。加持寶樓閣<note n="0311004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔印〕－【甲】</note><app n="0311004"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0311b03"/>印二手金剛掌真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0311b04"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">引一</note>唵薩&CB00085;他欠<note place="inline">二</note>鄔娜
<lb n="0311b05"/>哦<note place="inline">二合</note>帝薩頗<note place="inline">二合</note>囉呬<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00805;<note place="inline">三</note>哦哦那檢娑&CB00085;
<lb n="0311b06"/><note place="inline">二合</note>訶<note place="inline">引四</note></p>
<lb n="0311b07"/><p>次結佛頂輪王印。二掌內相叉作拳。&CB00594;二光
<lb n="0311b08"/>屈上節如劍。並&CB00594;二輪屈二蓋兩節。相拄於
<lb n="0311b09"/>二輪上。印五處加護真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0311b10"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>步嚕唵<note place="inline">三合二</note></p>
<lb n="0311b11"/><p>次結網橛印。准前根本印。屈二蓋上節。背不
<lb n="0311b12"/>相著。以二輪各壓。上下揮轉。即成結上下界
<lb n="0311b13"/>真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0311b14"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>阿&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底呵多舍
<lb n="0311b15"/>娑娜南<note place="inline">二</note>唵<note place="inline">引三</note>微枳囉拏微特防<note place="inline">去聲二合</note>娑尼<note place="inline">四</note>
<lb n="0311b16"/>迦比羅貳縛里尼<note place="inline">五</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>娑耶<note place="inline">六</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0311b17"/>合</note>吠賒薩帝呶<note place="inline">引</note>囉特縛<note place="inline">二合七</note>能<note place="inline">上聲</note>瑟吒囉<note place="inline">三合</note>
<lb n="0311b18"/>囉乞沙<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00805;癹<note place="inline"><note n="0311005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">八＋（吽）&M062403;本文【甲】</note><app n="0311005"><lem>八</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">八吽</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0311b19"/><p>次結牆印。准前根本印。屈二蓋兩節相逼。平
<lb n="0311b20"/>&CB00594;二輪附二蓋。右旋三匝即成。金剛牆界真
<lb n="0311b21"/>言曰<note place="inline">歸命同前</note>。</p>
<lb n="0311b22"/><p type="dharani">噁<note place="inline">引一</note>莫壑<note place="inline">二</note></p>
<lb n="0311b23"/><p>次結車輅印。二手內相叉。仰掌申二蓋。令甲
<lb n="0311b24"/>側相拄。屈二輪拄蓋根下。想於他方世界奉
<lb n="0311b25"/>迎本尊。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0311b26"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引一</note>&CB00418;嚕&CB00418;嚕吽<note place="inline">二</note></p>
<lb n="0311b27"/><p>次結迎輅印。准車輅印。以二輪撥光頭。向身
<lb n="0311b28"/>三招。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0311b29"/><p type="dharani">發遣除羯哩灑<note place="inline">二合</note>耶加尾薩哩惹耶</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0954B.0311c" n="0311c"/>
<lb n="0311c01"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>薩底哩野<note place="inline"><note n="0311006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝四【甲】</note><app n="0311006"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">四</rdg></app>合</note>地尾<note place="inline">二合</note>迦南<note place="inline">一</note>怛他孽
<lb n="0311c02"/>哆南<note place="inline">二</note>唵<note place="inline">引三</note>&CB00085;日啷<note place="inline">二合</note>儗<note place="inline">愚以切</note>&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二<note n="0311007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（引）【甲】</note><app n="0311007"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">合引</rdg></app></note>羯
<lb n="0311c03"/>哩灑耶娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引四</note></p>
<lb n="0311c04"/><p>次結迎請印。准前根本印。屈右蓋於光後。向
<lb n="0311c05"/>前三招。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0311c06"/><p type="dharani">娜謨婆&CB00344;&CB00085;帝<note place="inline">一</note>阿&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底呵&CB00418;瑟尼<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0311c07"/>沙耶<note place="inline">二</note>翳呬翳<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0311008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娑＝呬婆【甲】</note><app n="0311008"><lem>娑</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">呬婆</rdg></app>&CB00344;刎<note place="inline">三</note>達麼囉惹<note place="inline">平聲</note>&CB00425;
<lb n="0311c08"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底<note n="0311009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">車＝掣【甲】＊</note><app n="0311009"><lem>車</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">掣</rdg></app><note place="inline">鴟奚切</note>南<note place="inline">四</note>遏鉗巘談補瑟貶<note place="inline">逋諳切</note>度
<lb n="0311c09"/>貶<note place="inline">同上</note>末&CB00444;&CB00135;半者<note place="inline">五</note>滿遮避洛乞叉<note place="inline">二合六</note>阿&CB00425;
<lb n="0311c10"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底呵多<note place="inline">七</note>麼囉&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">引</note>羯囉<note place="inline">二合</note>麼耶娑
<lb n="0311c11"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引八</note></p>
<lb n="0311c12"/><p>次結一切<note n="0311010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">辨＝辦【甲】</note><app n="0311010"><lem>辨</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">辦</rdg></app>事佛頂印。二手內相叉。&CB00594;二光
<lb n="0311c13"/>如幢。諸供養物及浴水洗淨土等。並用此真
<lb n="0311c14"/>言。加持辟除去垢結界皆用此真言。左旋辟
<lb n="0311c15"/>除右旋結界真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0311c16"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三滿多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>唵<note place="inline">引二</note>吒嚕<note n="0311011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚕＝唵【甲】</note><app n="0311011"><lem>嚕</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">唵</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合三</note>滿
<lb n="0311c17"/>馱娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引四</note></p>
<lb n="0311c18"/><p>次重結前網橛印。結上方界。</p>
<lb n="0311c19"/><p>次結阿娑莽倪<note place="inline">移枳切</note>尼印。側二手。左掩右。<note n="0311012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">堅＝&CB00594;【甲】</note><app n="0311012"><lem>堅</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00594;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0311c20"/>二輪右轉一匝。即成密縫真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0311c21"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引一</note>阿娑莽倪尼吽癹<note place="inline">二</note></p>
<lb n="0311c22"/><p>次結獻閼伽印。准前根本印。屈二蓋相拄。附
<lb n="0311c23"/>二光。&CB00594;二輪各附蓋根側真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0311c24"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>唵<note place="inline">引二</note>閼伽囉訶<note place="inline">三</note>閼
<lb n="0311c25"/>伽必哩<note place="inline">二合</note>野<note place="inline">四</note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底<app type="＊" source="0311009"><lem>車</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">掣</rdg></app><note place="inline">鴟奚切</note>娜末鉗娑
<lb n="0311c26"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引五</note></p>
<lb n="0311c27"/><p>次重結根本印。</p>
<lb n="0311c28"/><p>次結獻師子座印。准前根本印。屈二蓋於二
<lb n="0311c29"/>輪甲側。真言曰。</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0954B.0312a" n="0312a"/>
<lb n="0312a01"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引一</note>阿者囉尾囉耶娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引二</note></p>
<lb n="0312a02"/><p>次結塗香印。准前根本印。屈右蓋。倚於右光
<lb n="0312a03"/>下節真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0312a04"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>唵<note place="inline">引二</note>怛&CB00769;<note place="inline">二合</note>盧枳
<lb n="0312a05"/>也<note place="inline">二合</note>獻馱孽帝<note place="inline">三</note>吽吽癹癹娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引四</note></p>
<lb n="0312a06"/><p>次結獻華印。准前塗香印。改左蓋。倚<note n="0312001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">右＝左【甲】</note><app n="0312001"><lem>右</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">左</rdg></app>光
<lb n="0312a07"/>下節真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0312a08"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>唵<note place="inline">引二</note>薩&CB00085;盧迦補瑟
<lb n="0312a09"/>波<note place="inline">二合</note>步哆耶<note place="inline">三</note>吽吽癹癹娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引四</note></p>
<lb n="0312a10"/><p>次結燒香印。准前根本印。屈二蓋。各倚於光
<lb n="0312a11"/>下節真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0312a12"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>唵<note place="inline">引二</note>尾囉孽哆微哦
<lb n="0312a13"/>哆度<note n="0312002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">麼＝跛【甲】</note><app n="0312002"><lem>麼</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">跛</rdg></app>耶<note place="inline">三</note>吽吽癹癹娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引四</note></p>
<lb n="0312a14"/><p>次結獻食印。准前根本印。屈二蓋上節。各附
<lb n="0312a15"/>於輪側真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0312a16"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>唵<note place="inline">引二</note>薩&CB00085;盧迦麼里
<lb n="0312a17"/>必哩<note place="inline">二合</note>夜耶<note place="inline">三</note>吽吽癹癹娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引四</note></p>
<lb n="0312a18"/><p>次結獻燈明印。准前根本印。屈二蓋兩節令
<lb n="0312a19"/>不相著二輪各附於蓋上真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0312a20"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>唵<note place="inline">引二</note>薩&CB00085;盧迦珊捺
<lb n="0312a21"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>捨娜耶<note place="inline">三</note>吽吽癹癹娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引四</note></p>
<lb n="0312a22"/><p>次結普供養加持印。二手虛心合掌。五頂各
<lb n="0312a23"/>兩節相交真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0312a24"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>薩&CB00085;勃馱冒地薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>南<note place="inline">一</note>唵<note place="inline">引二</note>
<lb n="0312a25"/>薩&CB00085;怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>僧俱蘇弭多<note place="inline">三</note>避吉惹囉<note n="0312003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">始＋（寧）【甲】</note><app n="0312003"><lem>始</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">始寧</rdg></app>那
<lb n="0312a26"/>慕薩低娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引四</note></p>
<lb n="0312a27"/><p>次結遍照佛頂印。二手內相叉合為拳。令二
<lb n="0312a28"/>光節微起真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0312a29"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>噁<note place="inline">引二</note>莫含<note place="inline">呼頷切三</note></p>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0954B.0312b" n="0312b"/>
<lb n="0312b01"/><p>次結白傘蓋佛頂印。二輪各捻二高甲上。側
<lb n="0312b02"/>相合。二蓋屈如蓋形。二光微屈相合。二勝各
<lb n="0312b03"/>&CB00594;相合真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0312b04"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>阿&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底呵多舍
<lb n="0312b05"/>娑娜南<note place="inline">二</note>唵<note place="inline">引三</note>麼麼麼吽匿<note place="inline">&CB00135;翼切四</note></p>
<lb n="0312b06"/><p>次結光聚佛頂印。准前白傘蓋印。坼開二蓋
<lb n="0312b07"/>真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0312b08"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>阿&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底呵多舍
<lb n="0312b09"/>娑娜南<note place="inline">二</note>唵<note place="inline">引三</note>怛他&CB00617;都瑟尼<note place="inline">二合</note>沙<note place="inline">四</note>阿娜
<lb n="0312b10"/>&CB00085;盧枳多慕&CB00069;馱<note place="inline">二合五</note>帝儒囉始吽<note place="inline">六</note>入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0312b11"/>&CB00256;入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00256;<note place="inline">七</note>馱迦馱迦<note place="inline">八</note>娜囉微娜囉<note place="inline">九</note>瞋
<lb n="0312b12"/>那牝那吽吽癹癹娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引十</note></p>
<lb n="0312b13"/><p>次結高佛頂印。准前白傘蓋印。屈二蓋拄二
<lb n="0312b14"/>光中節背真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0312b15"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>阿&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底呵多舍
<lb n="0312b16"/>娑娜南<note place="inline">二</note>唵<note place="inline">引三</note>&CB00135;&CB01328;&CB00135;卑渝<note place="inline">二合</note>娜哦都瑟尼
<lb n="0312b17"/><note place="inline">二合</note>沙<note place="inline">四</note>吽吽癹癹娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引五</note></p>
<lb n="0312b18"/><p>次結勝佛頂印。准高佛頂印。移二蓋向上。兩
<lb n="0312b19"/>穬麥許真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0312b20"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>阿&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底呵多舍
<lb n="0312b21"/>娑娜南<note place="inline">二</note>唵<note place="inline">引三</note>入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>羅惹踰瑟尼<note place="inline">二合</note>沙<note place="inline">四</note>
<lb n="0312b22"/>吽癹娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引五</note></p>
<lb n="0312b23"/><p>次結摧毀佛頂<note place="inline">尾枳囉拏</note>印。二手內相叉作拳。&CB00594;二
<lb n="0312b24"/>光屈上節。右光拄左光面。令出半節許真言
<lb n="0312b25"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0312b26"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>阿&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底呵多舍
<lb n="0312b27"/>娑娜南<note place="inline">二</note>唵<note place="inline">引三</note>尾枳囉那<note place="inline">四</note>度那度那犢<note place="inline">引五</note></p>
<lb n="0312b28"/><p>次結摧碎佛頂印。並准前。改左光拄右光面。
<lb n="0312b29"/>亦出半節許。真言曰。</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0954B.0312c" n="0312c"/>
<lb n="0312c01"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>阿&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底呵多舍
<lb n="0312c02"/>娑娜南<note place="inline">二</note>唵<note place="inline">引二</note>阿&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底呵都瑟尼<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0312c03"/>沙耶<note place="inline">四</note>薩&CB00085;尾伽那<note place="inline">二合</note>尾<note n="0312004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">持＝特【甲】</note><app n="0312004"><lem>持</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">特</rdg></app>望<note place="inline">二合</note>娑那迦
<lb n="0312c04"/>囉耶<note place="inline">五</note>怛嚧<note place="inline">二合</note>吒耶娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引六</note></p>
<lb n="0312c05"/><p>次結輪王佛頂心印。准前根本印。屈二蓋拄
<lb n="0312c06"/>二光上節<note n="0312005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">節＝背【甲】</note><app n="0312005"><lem>節</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">背</rdg></app>上真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0312c07"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>阿&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底呵多舍
<lb n="0312c08"/>娑娜南<note place="inline">二</note>唵<note place="inline">引三</note>怛他<note n="0312006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">薩那＝&CB00617;都【甲】</note><app n="0312006"><lem>薩那</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00617;都</rdg></app>瑟尼<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0312007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">沙＋（阿）【甲】</note><app n="0312007"><lem>沙</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">沙阿</rdg></app>那&CB00085;
<lb n="0312c09"/>盧枳多<note place="inline">四</note>沒馱尼斫羯囉<note place="inline">二合</note>靺&CB00069;底<note place="inline">二合五</note>吽入
<lb n="0312c10"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>羅入&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>羅<note place="inline">六</note>馱迦馱迦<note place="inline">七</note>度那微度
<lb n="0312c11"/>那<note place="inline">八</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>娑耶麼囉逾瑳囉耶<note place="inline">九</note>呵那呵那
<lb n="0312c12"/><note place="inline">十</note>伴惹伴惹<note place="inline">十一</note>暗<note n="0312008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">音＝惡【甲】</note><app n="0312008"><lem>音</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">惡</rdg></app><note n="0312009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB03543;＋（十二）夾註【甲】</note><app n="0312009"><lem>&CB03543;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB03543;<note place="inline">十二</note></rdg></app>&CB00425;嚨<note place="inline">二合<note n="0312010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔十二〕－【甲】</note><app n="0312010"><lem>十二</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>企尼君
<lb n="0312c13"/>吒哩尼<note place="inline">十三</note>阿&CB00425;囉爾多薩怛囉馱哩尼<note place="inline">十四</note>吽
<lb n="0312c14"/>癹娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引十五</note></p>
<lb n="0312c15"/><p>次結心<note n="0312011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">中＋（心）【甲】</note><app n="0312011"><lem>中</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">中心</rdg></app>印。准前根本印。屈二蓋加於二光
<lb n="0312c16"/>上節上真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0312c17"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>阿&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">一合</note>底呵多舍
<lb n="0312c18"/>娑娜南<note place="inline">二</note>唵<note place="inline">引三</note>阿&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">引</note>爾多特<note place="inline">地翼切四</note></p>
<lb n="0312c19"/><p>普通諸佛頂印。二手虛心<note n="0312012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔金剛〕&M062403;－【甲】</note><app n="0312012"><lem>金剛</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>合掌。如華在
<lb n="0312c20"/>掌中。行者若&CB00229;遽不能遍結諸佛頂印。但結
<lb n="0312c21"/>此印誦諸佛頂真言。次結頂印。准前根本印。
<lb n="0312c22"/>屈右蓋&CB00594;。於右光後。令不相著真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0312c23"/><p type="dharani">娜<app type="＊" source="0311003"><lem>謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>三漫多勃馱南<note place="inline">一</note>阿&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底呵多舍
<lb n="0312c24"/>娑娜南<note place="inline">二</note>唵<note place="inline">引三</note>斫羯囉<note place="inline">二合</note>靺&CB00069;底<note place="inline">二合</note>唵吽<note place="inline">四</note></p>
<lb n="0312c25"/><p>次結頭印。准前根本印。開二蓋各直&CB00594;於光
<lb n="0312c26"/>後。令不相著微屈真言曰<note place="inline">歸命同前</note>。</p>
<lb n="0312c27"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引一</note>斫羯囉<note place="inline">二合</note>靺&CB00069;底<note place="inline">二合二</note>吽癹娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶
<lb n="0312c28"/><note place="inline">引三</note></p>
<lb n="0312c29"/><p>次又結根本印。</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0954B.0313a" n="0313a"/>
<lb n="0313a01"/><p>次結大三昧耶印。加護本尊。二手內相叉。&CB00594;
<lb n="0313a02"/>二光。屈二蓋於光後如鉤。相去一穬麥許。二
<lb n="0313a03"/>輪各附蓋根下。右旋三匝真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0313a04"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引一</note>商羯哩<note place="inline">二</note>摩訶三昧鹽娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引三</note></p>
<lb n="0313a05"/><p>次誦一百八名讚歎。</p>
<lb n="0313a06"/><p>欲念誦。先以五支成本尊。或五相成本尊瑜
<lb n="0313a07"/>伽。或於<note n="0313001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">處＝三【甲】</note><app n="0313001"><lem>處</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">三</rdg></app>處<note place="inline">頂舌心也</note>想一字頂輪。成本尊坐八
<lb n="0313a08"/>葉蓮華。於一一葉上想七寶。<note n="0313002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">准＝唯【甲】</note><app n="0313002"><lem>准</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">唯</rdg></app>前蓮華葉
<lb n="0313a09"/>上想佛眼尊。次應持珠<note place="inline">此依菩提場所說經</note>。</p>
<lb n="0313a10"/><p>次持珠合掌。捧珠誦清珠真言七遍真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0313a11"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引一</note>阿娜步<note place="inline">二合</note>低尾惹曳<note place="inline">而<note n="0313003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">矣＝奚【甲】</note><app n="0313003"><lem>矣</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">奚</rdg></app>切二</note>悉地悉馱囉
<lb n="0313a12"/>梯娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引三</note></p>
<lb n="0313a13"/><p>次結持珠印。二手各以輪捻高甲。直&CB00594;二光
<lb n="0313a14"/>二勝。屈二蓋於光後。令不相著<note place="inline">如毘盧遮那經半金剛杵印</note>
<lb n="0313a15"/>真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0313a16"/><p type="dharani">娜謨婆&CB00344;&CB00085;底<note place="inline">一</note>蘇悉第娑馱耶<note place="inline">二</note>悉馱囉梯
<lb n="0313a17"/>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline">引三</note></p>
<lb n="0313a18"/><lg><l>次應淨其心</l><l>如法而念誦</l>
<lb n="0313a19"/><l>持珠令當心</l><l>繫心於鼻端</l>
<lb n="0313a20"/><l>字句分明呼</l><l>不緩亦不急</l>
<lb n="0313a21"/><l>不頻伸噦嗌</l><l>咳嗽與唾涕</l>
<lb n="0313a22"/><l>染等心相應</l><l>及心緣苦受</l>
<lb n="0313a23"/><l>如是等過患</l><l>皆不得成就</l></lg>
<lb n="0313a24"/><p>當念誦時。身心不得疲怠。若勞倦即應結五
<lb n="0313a25"/>供養印。誦讚歎獻閼伽。念誦畢持珠頂上。次
<lb n="0313a26"/>結前密縫印。左轉一匝即成解界。</p>
<lb n="0313a27"/><p>次結奉送印。准前根本印。左蓋外擲。誦迎請
<lb n="0313a28"/>真言。除翳呬翳呬。加孽車孽車句。即成奉送。
<lb n="0313a29"/>次應復結牆及網橛等印。加護處上下及所
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0954B.0313b" n="0313b"/>
<lb n="0313b01"/>成就物。次結計里枳里印。左輪壓勝甲上。餘
<lb n="0313b02"/>三指頂坼開直&CB00594;。如三股杵形。右旋轉三匝
<lb n="0313b03"/>成結界真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0313b04"/><p type="dharani">唵<note place="inline">引一</note>枳里枳里&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>吽癹<note place="inline">二</note></p>
<lb n="0313b05"/><p>次結軍吒利印。二勝於掌中交。屈二高壓。
<lb n="0313b06"/>以二輪壓高上。&CB00594;二光相合。屈二蓋於光
<lb n="0313b07"/>後。令一麥許不相著。右旋三匝即成結界真
<lb n="0313b08"/>言曰。</p>
